               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183904080019"></xptr>
               <p>one in his basket—he said it was a bit of sweeping, and he took it because the wages they had did not keep them—I said, "Have you taken any be<lb></lb>fore?"—he said he had once before, and sold it to a man in Rosemary-lane at 2<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. a pound—it is worth 8<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. a pound—I said I would go there—he then said he did not know the place—that it was a man he used to meet at a public-house.</p>
